## Including Plots

When you click the **Knit** button a [document](#r-markdown) will be generated that includes both content as well as[^4] the output of any embedded R code chunks within the document. You can embed an R code chunk like this:

[^4]: here we goafd asdfasdf asdfdsasfasfasdfdsa

You can also embed plots, for example:

```{r pressure, echo=FALSE}
plot(pressure)
```

Note that the `echo = FALSE` parameter was added to the code chunk to prevent printing of the R code that generated the plot.
